data.description: Welcome to the quaint river city of Green Cove Springs and this newly renovated, affordable, and conveniently located home. Enjoy the spacious kitchen with new stylish Shaker style cabinets accented by stainless steel appliances, decorative floating shelves and fashionable shiplap. Enjoy the Florida outdoors on the rear deck shaded by one of the areas largest rain trees.The large backyard offers privacy rarely found in the city and is perfect for entertaining. There is durable tile throughout the common areas & bathrooms with carpet in the bedrooms.  Updated HVAC, wiring, plumbing, new ceiling fans and light fixtures. Located just minutes from boat ramps, Spring Park, St Vincent Hospital, and is an easy commute to NAS, Jacksonville or St Augustine
